Fetches the GeneSetDb from MultiGSEAResult

MultiGSEAResult-utilities.Rd

Fetches the GeneSetDb from MultiGSEAResult

geneSetDb(x)

Arguments

x

MultiGSEAResult

Value

The GeneSetDb

Examples

vm <- exampleExpressionSet(do.voom=TRUE)
gdb <- exampleGeneSetDb()
mg <- multiGSEA(gdb, vm, vm$design, 'tumor', methods=NULL)
geneSetDb(mg)
